<P>THE FARCE OF THE VILLAGE LAWYER.</P>
<P>IN TWO ACTS.</P>
<P>AS PERFORMED AT THE THEATRE-ROYAL, <HI>SMOKE-ALLEY.</HI></P>
<P>M, DCC, XCII.</P>
<P>PRINTED FOR THE BOOKSELLERS&punc;</P>
</DIV1>
